  $ touch ../$AUTOENV_FILE_LEAVE
  $ autoenv-edit
  Note: found ../.autoenv.zsh, but AUTOENV_LOOK_UPWARDS is disabled.
  Note: found ../.autoenv_leave.zsh, but AUTOENV_LOOK_UPWARDS is disabled.
